videos.description: Udoka Azubuike hauls in a pass from Marcus Garrett and bullies his way to the hoop for an and-1 basket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Azubuike fights for an early and-1) 2020/3/4

videos.headline: Azubuike fights for an early and-1

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike takes the alley-oop lob from Marcus Garrett and finishes at the rim with a powerful jam.

videos.headline: Azubuike's first dunk of the night forces a TCU timeout

videos.description: Ochai Agbaji threads a pass over TCU defenders and up to the hoop for an Udoka Azubuike slam.

videos.description: Kansas can't stop Edric Dennis from 3-point range as he pulls up for his fourth 3-pointer of the half.

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike is there for a powerful putback off of Devon Dotson's miss.

videos.description: Desmond Bane fakes out Udoka Azubuike leaving him wide-open for a 3-pointer.

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike checks out of the game in the final minute of Kansas' senior night win over TCU, hugging coach Bill Self on his way back to the bench.
